<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Home - Sals Educational Academy</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="/logo.png" type="text/x-icon">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/style.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Montserrat:wght@400;600&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <nav>
            <div class="container">
                <h1 class="logo"><a href="#">Sals Educational Academy</a></h1>
                <ul>
                    <li><a href="#">Home</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">About Us</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Programs</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Admissions</a></li>
                    <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </nav>
        <div class="hero">
            <div class="container">
                <h1>Welcome to Sals Educational Academy</h1>
                <p>Empowering Students for a Brighter Future</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Learn More</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </header>
    <main>
        <section class="about">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>About Us</h2>
                <p>Sals Educational Academy is dedicated to providing quality education and fostering the holistic development of students. Our experienced faculty and comprehensive programs ensure that each student achieves their full potential.</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="programs">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Our Programs</h2>
                <div class="program-cards">
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Primary Education</h3>
                        <p>Building a strong foundation for young learners with engaging and interactive lessons.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Secondary Education</h3>
                        <p>Preparing students for higher education and future careers with a robust curriculum.</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="card">
                        <h3>Extracurricular Activities</h3>
                        <p>Encouraging students to explore their interests and talents through various activities.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="admissions">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Admissions</h2>
                <p>Join our academy and embark on a journey of academic excellence and personal growth. Click below to learn more about our admission process and criteria.</p>
                <a href="#" class="btn">Apply Now</a>
            </div>
        </section>
        <section class="contact">
            <div class="container">
                <h2>Contact Us</h2>
                <p>If you have any questions or need further information, feel free to reach out to us.</p>
                <form action="/contact" method="POST">
                    <input type="text" name="name" placeholder="Your Name" required>
                    <input type="email" name="email" placeholder="Your Email" required>
                    <textarea name="message" placeholder="Your Message" required></textarea>
                    <button type="submit" class="btn">Send Message</button>
                </form>
            </div>
        </section>
    </main>
    <footer>
        <div class="container">
            <p>&copy; 2024 Sals Educational Academy. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
